ISLAMABAD, Aug 13 (APP): President Dr Arif Alvi has granted his approval to the National Information Technology Board (NITB) Bill 2022 under Article 75 of the Constitution of Pakistan.
Under the said bill, NITB would be established, President Secretariat Press Wing said in a press release on Saturday.
